---
title: Mexican Beef Tacos with Avocado Salsa
description:  It’s double or nothing with these tacos. There’s both beef strips, two delicious flavours of Tex-Mex and enchilada sauce
working together and double the fun with veggies like sweetcorn and avocado. More is sometimes the way to go!

*We’ve replaced the baby leaves in this recipe with shredded Cheddar Cheese due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as
delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67598b95daedc2bd1295a701-f305a81b.jpeg
